Class LogRouter.AbstractRouter

java.lang.Object
io.jstach.rainbowgum.LogRouter.AbstractRouter
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogEventLogger, LogLifecycle, LogRouter, LogRouter.Route, LogRouter.Router, AutoCloseable
Enclosing interface:
LogRouter
public abstract static non-sealed class LogRouter.AbstractRouter extends Object implements LogRouter.Router, LogRouter.Route
A user supplied router usually for filtering or transforming purposes. The method required to implement is transformOrNull(LogEvent).
